## Troubleshooting & Performance

### Common Issues
```bash
# SLO Display Error
Error: "SLOs showing as lecture titles"
Fix: Enhanced regex filtering in utils.py extract_syllabus_topics()

# Unicode Error  
Error: "ascii codec can't encode character"
Fix: UTF-8 encoding in generators.py response handling

# Button Duplicate Error
Error: "Multiple button elements with same ID"
Fix: Unique keys using filename_prefix in ui_components.py
```

