## Educational Philosophy & Differentiators

### Core Principles
1. **Pedagogical Soundness**: Grounded in educational theory and best practices
2. **Current Relevance**: Real-time integration of industry developments
3. **Student Engagement**: Multi-modal learning with interactive elements
4. **Assessment Alignment**: Backward design from clear learning outcomes
5. **Professional Quality**: Industry-standard course materials and formatting

### Key Differentiators from Generic ChatGPT
1. **Domain Expertise**: 10K+ educational document training vs general conversation
2. **Real-Time Context**: Live Serper API vs static training cutoff
3. **Institutional Intelligence**: Program-specific SLOs and compliance requirements
4. **Quality Assurance**: 4-criteria pedagogical evaluation vs no systematic review
5. **Continuous Learning**: Improvement from actual course outcomes vs static model
6. **Multi-Agent Specialization**: Purpose-built generators vs general-purpose model
7. **Assessment Integration**: Evidence-based evaluation tools vs generic responses

